What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Aircraft Evacuation Market?



Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Aircraft Evacuation Market

The aircraft evacuation market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 4.68% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on aircraft evacuation market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The high demand of the equipment at various aircraft sectors is escalating the growth of aircraft evacuation market.

An aircraft evacuation system refers to the type of the system that includes evacuation equipment. The equipment enables emergency evacuation from an aircraft that could take place on the ground or in water. The equipment is widely utilized for evacuation such as slides, personal floatation devices, ejection seats and life rafts among others.

The increase in demand for new aircraft across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of aircraft evacuation market. The rise in the integration of technologically robust aircraft evacuation system on the modern aircrafts by manufacturers, and surge in demand for commercial as well as defense aircrafts accelerate the market growth. The increase in demand for aircraft emergency landing equipment, and development of lightweight, and enhanced safety evacuation system by aircraft manufacturers and the evacuation systems manufacturers further influence the market. Additionally, surge in the investments, expansion of commercial aircraft, increase in safety regulations for aircraft, and concerns regarding the safety of passengers positively affect the aircraft evacuation market. Furthermore, technological advancements in the evacuation systems extend profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, concerns regarding long product lifecycle of evacuation slides, and existing backlogs of aircraft deliveries are expected to obstruct the market growth. The presence of stringent regulatory are projected to challenge the aircraft evacuation market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

